localizationDataList.Eng: Its shape sticks with you for no clear reason.
Rough texture that grips your hand nicely.
Chunky and solid just like it looks.
Smoky tones give it a subtle flair.
The chill has a strangely pleasant feel.
Tiny sparkles make it oddly playful.
Classic patterns draw just enough attention.

localizationDataList.Kor: 빛을 잘 받아서 눈에 잘 띈다.
localizationDataList.Eng: Catches the light just enough to be seen.

localizationDataList.Kor: 군데군데 금속이 박혀 있어 시선이 간다.
localizationDataList.Eng: Scattered metal bits keep it interesting.
Thick bones give it a weirdly sturdy vibe.
Every segment clicks just a little.

localizationDataList.Kor: 밝은 데선 보이고 어두운 데선 안 보인다.
